\s IGIHE NI KIBI, SHENGERO RY’IMANA.
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Igihe ni kibi, Shengero ry’Imana, Guma mw’Ijambo rya Yesu tugira dutahe. \bd*\bd Teg’ugutwi bwenge, wiya\bd*\bd mirize gipfu, Niwirind’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd umwambiro w’abafarisayo.\bd*
\pc \bdit Umuvugishwa\bdit*\bdit  w’igihe cacu yarashiz’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ijwi hejuru, \bdit*\bdit ngo \bdit*\bdit mwongera kumubamba\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit nko ku \bdit*\bdit Musaraba\bdit*\bdit .\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit Inyigisho z’amadini muzirutish’ivya Yesu, \bdit*\bdit mwongera \bdit*\bdit kumubamb’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit ubugira kabiri.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ibuk’aho bamubamba, ico bamuziza, ngo yigira Imana kand’azirur’isabato. Bari bahegekey’ibitabo vyabo, mugabo ntibahishuriwe Umwami uw’ari we.\bd*
\pc \bdit Umuvugishwa w’igihe cacu yarashiz’ ijwi hejuru, ngo mwongera kumubamba\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit nko ku Musaraba. Inyigisho z’amadini muzirutish’ivya Yesu, mwongera kumubamb’ ubugira kabiri.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Bamushikanye, I Nyagahanga, baramucurira kandi banamubambaho. Ub’abonekera, mw’Ijambo ryiwe, bongera ku mubamba, ko bank’ivy’ukuri.\bd*
\pc \bdit Umuvugishwa w’igihe cacu yarashiz’ ijwi hejuru, ngo mwongera kumubamba\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit nko ku Musaraba. Inyigisho z’amadini muzirutish’ivya Yesu, mwongera kumubamb’ ubugira kabiri.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ko batamumenye, mur’ico gihe, N’ubu shengero ntibonamumenya, ko batatahuye, abana b’Imana n’ub’Ishengero ryiwe ntiboritahura.\bd*
